{"tid":128040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師公會譴責辱罵法官言論","createTime":"2017-02-20T13:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T14:15:13.000Z","uid":41404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f855c791d72228954a140245e715eea91699dc2e","tid":128040,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:38:04.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】大律師公會譴責有人就七警案辱罵法官。<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會發聲明，譴責個別人士辱罵及威嚇法官，又對法官作人身攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n公會強調，即使人人享有言論自由，及可評論法官的判決，但這些辱罵的言論無助理性討論，反而損害法治社會中，大眾對法庭應有的尊重，更有可能構成藐視法庭。公會認為，持不同意見人士應以理性討論方式表達意見。"},{"pid":"c91c777b6e34a9b3b967f28bff5c04a8e5f350c2","tid":128040,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實而家個林定國乜料"},{"pid":"25e5f4bd99dcb26911be7f2f9704fc05fbb56047","tid":128040,"uid":21706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"叫警犬拘捕佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba8daba9e86a4bad287fb6778021afd2950fe88","tid":128040,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:44:21.000Z","msg":"算啦<br />\n香港港治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e83718e7e86eb25bfce278380fae2ca0405893","tid":128040,"uid":63618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"其實已經判左有罪，然後仲籌錢/遊行支持佢地既算唔算支持人地犯罪？"},{"pid":"5a759526fbf7b73d3c456afcc3b2c87d2558ea83","tid":128040,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/